          "ADD-RES": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "In Addition to the Isomeric Ratios from the Charged",
                "Particle Induced Reaction the Paper Contains Isomeric",
                "Ratios from Thermal Neutron Induced Fission of U-233",
                "And U-235. The Results are (3.0+-0.5)For the Reaction",
                "92-U-233(N,F)61-Pm-148-M/G and (2.6+0.9-0.5) For the",
                "Reaction 92-U-235(N,F)61-Pm-148-M/G.",
                "Values For the Average Intrinsic Spin of the Primary",
                "Fragments are Deduced from the Isomeric Ratios, Using",
                "A Simple Statistical-Model Analysis.",
                "From the Individual Formation Cross Sections the",
                "Independent Fractional Chain Yield For Pm-148 and the",
                "Most Probable Charge For the Mass 148 Chain is Deduced"
              ]
            }
